@startuml
actor StudentsAndTeachers as User
participant ScrapApplication as SA
participant Administrator as Admin
participant Asset as Asset

activate User
User->>SA: 创建报废申请
activate SA
SA->Asset : 确认可用
activate Asset
Asset -> SA : 返回状态为可用
deactivate Asset
SA->>SA: 设置状态为等待批准
SA-->>User: 返回申请成功，正在等待
deactivate SA
deactivate User

Note over Admin, SA: 审批阶段
SA->>Admin: 通知新报废申请
Admin->>SA: 批准申请
activate SA
SA->>SA: 设置状态为通过
SA->>Asset: 设置状态为已报废
activate Asset
Asset-->>SA: 返回状态已更新
deactivate Asset
SA-->>Admin: 返回批准完成
deactivate SA

SA->>User: 返回批准
SA ->> Asset: 指定时间指定地点报废
@enduml